description:
The Childcare Bassinet allows you to enjoy more peaceful moments from nap time to bedtime. The mesh sides mean your baby is visible at your eye level. This breathable fabric is also made to promote airflow, giving a baby a cooler and comfortable space to rest. This bassinet is a dream for parents and babies.

  • Sturdy lightweight steel frame
  • Includes mattress pad 765 x 415 x 30mm with a fitted sheet
  • Mesh Ventilation
  • Simple assembly - no tools required
  • Suitability: Birth - 5 months
  • Product Dimensions: L: 805mm x W: 585mm x H: 790mm
  • Inside Bassinet:  L: 765mm x W: 415mm x H: 310mm
  • Weight: 6.4 kgs
name: Childcare 1EA
